al to t**-4, far steeper than the rate observed earlier,\nsuggesting that the primary shock has overrun the edge of a pre-SN wind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2012 08:27:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
