hift range. We conclude that\nobservations cannot yet rule out the possibility that the local universe is\nunder-dense at z<0.1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2012 11:27:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2012 12:04:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
